<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>HUAHUI · 工具入口</title>
<style>
:root {
  --primary: #d61f1f;
  --primary-strong: #9f1111;
  --text: #1c1714;
  --muted: #75675f;
  --border: #e0d5cd;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{
  margin:0; min-height:100vh;
  font-family:'Segoe UI Variable Text','Microsoft YaHei UI','PingFang SC',sans-serif;
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(214,31,31,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(214,31,31,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(214,31,31,0.10), transparent 34%),
    linear-gradient(180deg,#f8f4ef 0%,#ece6e1 100%);
  background-size:28px 28px,28px 28px,auto,auto;
  color:var(--text);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;
}
.card{
  background:rgba(255,252,249,0.95);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  border-radius:22px;
  box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(46,29,20,0.12);
  padding:34px 38px 30px;
  width:100%;max-width:460px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
}
.card::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:4px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--primary) 0%,#f36b55 58%,#1c1714 100%);
}
.brand-tag{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.66);
  border:1px solid rgba(214,31,31,0.18);
  font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--primary-strong);font-weight:800;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.brand-tag::before{content:"";width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),#ff7b6b);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(214,31,31,0.18);}
h1{
  margin:0 0 6px;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.06em;
  font-family:'Bahnschrift SemiCondensed','Segoe UI Variable Display','Microsoft YaHei UI',sans-serif;
}
.sub{margin:0 0 22px;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:0.04em;}
.entry{
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;
  padding:14px 18px;
  background:#fff;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:14px;
  color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;
  transition:transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, border-color .2s ease;
}
.entry:hover{
  transform:translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow:0 14px 28px rgba(46,29,20,0.10);
  border-color:rgba(214,31,31,0.32);
}
.entry .name{font-weight:800;font-size:1.02rem;letter-spacing:0.02em;}
.entry .meta{font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.06em;}
.entry .arrow{
  width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary) 0%,#a81212 100%);
  color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-weight:800;font-size:1rem;
  box-shadow:0 8px 16px rgba(168,18,18,0.22);
}
.foot{margin-top:18px;text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.08em;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <span class="brand-tag">HUAHUI</span>
    <h1>淋浴房工具</h1>
    <p class="sub">钻石型 · HY-050 · 打样版本</p>
    <a class="entry" href="./111.html">
      <div>
        <div class="name">淋浴房计算器</div>
        <div class="meta">拉图拉尺 · 玻璃下单尺寸</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow">›</div>
    </a>
    <div class="foot">© HUAHUI</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
